# Martenweave Workbench — environment variables
#
# No runtime environment variables are required. When the Workbench is served
# by `martenweave workbench`, the UI talks to the co-hosted local API on the
# same origin. In standalone development (`npm run dev`), the UI falls back to
# a local API at http://127.0.0.1:8000 and, when no API is reachable, to a
# small bundled offline sample in src/data.js.
#
# To point the dev server at a different API origin, set:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
